-- Putin Says Russian Bribery Shows People Have Money to Spend
-- B y   L y u b o v   P r o n i n a
-- 2011-12-15T09:19:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/putin-says-russian-bribery-shows-people-have-money-to-spend.html
Prime Minister  Vladimir Putin  said
the positive side of bribery in  Russia  is it shows that people
have money to spend.  Putin was speaking in his annual call-in television show
from Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
